original_title: The Wiggles - Dorothy the Dinosaur's Party
overview: It's Dorothy's first ever DVD! Dorothy hosts a surprise party for Captain Feathersword and invites Wags the Dog, Henry the Octopus and Fairy Clare, Larissa, Lucia and baby Maria! You will be entertained by the Rosy Orchestra as Dorothy sings Swinging On A Swing, Dance A Cachuca and I Look In the Mirror! With 17 new songs, Dorothy the Dinosaur's party is the best party she has ever had!
title: The Wiggles - Dorothy the Dinosaur's Party
